data.text: Some of those consequences can be severe. Omicron is ripping through crews on cargo vessels, raising concerns that a surge in cases, coupled with China’s tightened quarantine requirements, could delay supply-chain stabilization for the shipping industry. https://t.co/zHsPDYgETJ
